## 1. Purpose

This template provides a structured framework for assessing and managing risks in {{ business_name }}'s AI supply chain. It covers vendor inventories, sub-processor mapping, model provider assessments, data flow documentation, and annual audit procedures. This template aligns with **APP 8** (cross-border disclosure), **AI6 Guidance for AI Adoption** (Practice 6: Provide appropriate transparency), and **OAIC guidance on privacy and AI** (October 2024).

---

## 2. Scope

This audit template applies to all third-party AI tool vendors, sub-processors, AI model providers, open-source AI models, cloud infrastructure providers hosting AI workloads, and data annotation or training data service providers used by {{ business_name }}.

