### 4.2 Sub-Processor Requirements

All AI vendor contracts must include: obligation to disclose all current sub-processors before contract execution; 30 days advance notice before engaging new sub-processors; right for {{ business_name }} to object; flow-down of data protection obligations; and equivalent audit rights for sub-processors.

